Christian Le Guillochet https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christian_Le_Guillochet 0 Christian Le Guillochet (20 September 1933 in Albi – 10 February 2011 in Paris) was a French actor, playwright and theatre director. With his wife Luce Berthommé, he created the cultural center Lucernaire in Paris.
